**Summary:** A new autoregressive model variant with a trainable order-policy for sequence generation of high-dimensional unordered data achieves state-of-the-art performance in molecular graph generation.

## 5. Autoregressive Boltzmann Generators
**arxiv_id:** 2606.27361 | **upvotes:** 0
https://huggingface.co/papers/2606.27361
**Keywords:** Boltzmann Generators, normalizing flows, autoregressive modelling, sequential inference, Large Language Models
**Summary:** Autoregressive Boltzmann Generators overcome limitations of normalizing flows in molecular system sampling by enabling sequential inference and improved scalability through language model architectures.

